ActNational Capital Act
SubjectPaul's Boat Lines Ltd. - Concession Agreement.
PrecisApproval for the National Capital Commission to grant a lease longer than five years by granting a two-year extension, starting January 1, 2011, to an existing five-year concession agreement for the operation of a boat tour service on the Ottawa River.
